com.tsgrp.migration.queuepop

Class QueuePopulatorFileFolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.queuepop.QueuePopulatorFileFolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PipelinePopulateQueueEventListener

    public class QueuePopulatorFileFolder
extends AbstractListener
implements PipelinePopulateQueueEventListener
    A simple filesystem queue populator. It takes one argument, a folder path, and it adds all the files in that folder (and its subfolders). The sourceId will be the filename, like file.txt, or the relative filename (like subFolder1/file.txt) for subfolders
